Sophisticated computational representation based on the "Conspiracy theory" of a flat earth, consisting of a circular flat surface and two orbs circulating in a variable trajectory throughout the year and surrounded by a huge wall of ice guarded by governments, this approach has gained popularity in recent years in different spheres of the population.

disclaimer: I am a fan of conspiracy theories, I am not necessarily a believer but I am fascinated by reading between the lines and looking for how much truth is hidden among the deliberate noise.

"Five hundred years ago, everybody knew the Earth was flat, and fifteen minutes ago, you knew that humans were alone on this planet. Imagine what you'll know tomorrow." - Agent Kay, 'MIB'
